Markose, šta se desilo?

294
00:59:24,721 --> 00:59:26,721
Prokleto sranje!

295
00:59:30,860 --> 00:59:32,860
Markose, koči! Koči!

296
00:59:39,569 --> 00:59:41,569
Jesi li dobro?

297
00:59:46,376 --> 00:59:48,376
Šta si to uradio?

298
